file_content.text: Tyth give me strength!
For my son!
You cannot have him.
Arcann will live!
No! I must endure!
Izax is calling to me...
Fight with honor! K'oyacyi!
We need backup!
Stay together! Fight as one!
I'll hold the line. See you on the other side, Commander!
The Alliance never falls!
Clear a landing zone so reinforcements can join the fight!
Commander! Lana! Nice of you to join the party.
Theron. What's your status?
I can hold the Tower of Prophecy a bit longer, but the Alien Enclave could really use your help.
Reinforcements incoming!
We're on our way. To the bridge, Commander.
Heads up, Commander. We've got reports of a battle droid in your path. Looks like a big one.
We'll handle it. How are you doing?
Touch and go. The sooner we secure Voss-Ka, the better.
The droid's neutralized!
Stay close! Don't give it room to breathe!
Good, but our fight isn't over just yet.
Friendlies are pinned down on the northern plateau. They could use your help.
We're on our way. Hold your position and keep me updated.
Roger that, Commander.
Incoming! Get down!
It's gone...
Theron! Change of plans. They destroyed the northern plateau.
Wait, what?
We're coming to reinforce your position.
Find us another way to reach you.
Search the area. There must be some way to clear the gap.
Commander! They're hitting us hard. Don't know how much longer we can hold out.
Hold your ground, Theron. We're on our way.
I'll do my best.
Commander. Vaylin's forces are gunning for civilians near your location.
Are you mad? We can't save everyone!
It's your call, Commander. Sending coordinates.
Commander. Got a toy incoming for you.
Her name's Storm Rider. Hop in and take her for a spin.
You know me so well, Torian.
Make them hurt, Commander.
Happy hunting, cyar'ika.
Commander. Got a surprise incoming, just for you.
Good work, Torian.
People once traveled across the galaxy to see this shrine. Now look at it...
The force field's up and running.
Good. Now we hold our ground and buy Senya some time.
Stand down!
Look out! They've got missiles!
Head for these coordinates. Last I heard, some Voss commandos were cooking up a shortcut.
Is that a walker?
That was close.
The shrine is ours. Let's find Senya and Arcann--before it's too late.
Stop or we shoot!
Wait! It's the Alliance Commander!
Hurry inside. We'll cover you.
The force field's down!
Fall back! Now!
Grab those explosives! We can use them to collapse the tunnel behind us.
There's still time to save them.
Rokuss volunteered to save them. He's got more than enough support since you neutralized that Star Fortress.
Vaylin will answer for this.
We've got repair teams in the field. Find them, and they'll patch us up.
Barely a scratch on this thing. You're a natural, Commander!
You sure this thing's seen heavy combat? Where's the damage?
We'll get you up and running!
All right, team. Let's get it fixed!
Thing's barely standing... We'll do what we can!
You've really seen some action.
Good to go, Commander!
Good luck out there!
Be safe, Commander!
All patched up!
We're done. Rest is up to you!
Blast! It's too far to jump.
That's a bit more reasonable. I think we can jump across into that exposed tunnel.
This should do it. Let's hurry across the chasm.
